# MT5 Trader app — QR after every update

When you change code under `artifacts/mt5-trader/`:

1. Run `pnpm --filter @workspace/mt5-trader run typecheck` and fix errors.
2. Start an iOS preview build so the user gets a **new install QR / link**:
   ```bash
   cd artifacts/mt5-trader && npm_config_user_agent='pnpm/10.0.0' pnpm exec eas build --platform ios --profile preview --non-interactive
   ```
3. When the build finishes, surface the **expo.dev build URL** and QR from the command output (user installs on phone from that link).

Do not assume code edits alone update the installed app — there is no OTA configured.

For quick in-Expo-Go iteration only (not a new standalone install), `pnpm exec expo start --tunnel` shows a dev QR in Terminal faster; default to **EAS preview** unless the user asks for dev-only.
